data.description: ***WELCOME HOME***  This unrestricted privately secluded piece of Heaven is waiting for you and your family to snatch up and call it a day.  1.44 acre tract that has an abundance of live oaks as well as mature pecan trees throughout.  Bayou backs to the property serving as a rear boundary. Great drainage with all the privacy one could ask for.  Home has 3 bedrooms and 4 full bathrooms. Front covered porch enclosed and two sided rear covered porches, Large hot-tub, Water well is enclosed with ample storage. A 20X40 workshop that is very well built with heavier guage metal siding and round metal studs, Two Geothermal heating/cooling systems. Radio tower/Antemma for wideband radio frequency transmittal.  Come on out and see this place for yourself. You won't be dissappointed...
